                                            <hr/>
                                             <h4>Policy Renewals </h4>
                                             <p>At Inniti we make sure our risk managers take the required time to ponder over coverage proposals of insurers to help in effective planning and management of insurance renewals helping in eliminating any errors during the initial stage itself.</p>
